  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "What are the top ten PC games ever?",
  "response": "Determining the \"top ten\" PC games of all time can be subjective, as it depends on various factors such as personal preference, genre, and the era in which the games were released. However, based on critical acclaim, cultural impact, and enduring popularity, here is a list of ten highly regarded PC games:\n\n1. **World of Warcraft**\n   - Often cited as the most influential MMORPG ever, World of Warcraft has captivated millions of players worldwide since its release in 2004.\n\n2. **Minecraft**\n   - Known for its sandbox gameplay and limitless creativity, Minecraft has become a cultural phenomenon since its release in 2009.\n\n3. **The Witcher 3: Wild Hunt**\n   - Widely praised for its expansive open world, deep storytelling, and engaging gameplay, The Witcher 3 is considered one of the greatest RPGs of all time.\n\n4. **Half-Life 2**\n   - Renowned for its innovative physics engine and groundbreaking narrative, Half-Life 2 redefined first-person shooters upon its release in 2004.\n\n5. **Portal**\n   - Celebrated for its clever puzzle mechanics and witty storytelling, Portal has become a beloved classic since its release in 2007.\n\n6. **Sid Meier's Civilization V**\n   - A staple in the strategy genre, Civilization V is lauded for its deep gameplay and replayability, making it a favorite among strategy enthusiasts.\n\n7. **Starcraft II: Wings of Liberty**\n   - A cornerstone of the real-time strategy genre, Starcraft II has a robust competitive scene and is celebrated for its balanced gameplay and intricate mechanics.\n\n8. **Bioshock**\n   - Known for its immersive narrative and unique setting, Bioshock is praised for its innovative use of storytelling and atmospheric gameplay.\n\n9. **Diablo II**\n   - A legendary action RPG, Diablo II is renowned for its addictive gameplay loop and has been a fan favorite since its release in 2000.\n\n10. **Dota 2**\n    - A leading title in the MOBA genre, Dota 2 is celebrated for its strategic depth and competitive esports scene, captivating players globally since its release in 2013.\n\nThis list captures a range of genres and represents games that have had a significant impact on the PC gaming community.",
